🥑🥚Smashed Avo Toast with a beautiful poached egg🥑🥚 Great way to start the day 💗 ⁣
⁣
Drizzled some @woodlandtruffles white truffle oil onto sliced baguette and toasted them in the oven for 3 mins, topped them with smashed avos, red chilli pepper flakes, a poached egg and some truffle dust!⁣
⁣
What’s on your table today? ❤️⁣
